01:46.880 --> 01:49.600
Thank you so much for joining me here today, Joe.

01:49.600 --> 01:53.760
Chris is away, but never fear. He can't stop Linux Unplugged.

01:53.760 --> 01:55.360
Yeah, we must stop meeting like this.

01:55.360 --> 02:00.720
We must. You know, someday I think we will, and it will be a happy celebratory occasion.

02:00.720 --> 02:04.800
